headline: All Aboard: Agoda Unveils Asia's Most Scenic Train Journeys
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has released a curated list of Asia's most impressive train journeys, offering travelers a unique and authentic way to experience the continent's landscapes. These rail adventures turn transit into an attraction, offering a front-row seat to remote vistas that are often inaccessible by road or air.
